item.title: 401k
item.description: Have you ever wondered if you’re doing all the right things in your 401k for a secure retirement? In this video, we will go look at 8 things you should be doing in your 401k that will ensure your retirement savings to exceed one million dollars, and even show you ways to contribute up to $66,000 per year in your 401k.

item.title: Choosing funds in a 401k
item.description: Talk about how some people drop funds that are doing badly and choose funds that have recently done a lot better.
